He notes no chest pain , SOB , or diaphoresis during the event. Once he was conscious he called EMS for transport to the MCMC . Of note , he was here at the GGH about 6 weeks ago for a rule out MI , which was negative. Review of symptoms was significant for back pain associated with spinal stenosis.
